channel.title: Which of these names do you like the most for an RSPS name? Poll
channel.description:
[u][b]Introduction[/b][/u]
So I'm currently working on a name for my upcoming RSPS, I've managed to cut the list down to a decent shortlist of words that I believe may sound decent. I've also got 3 quick questions below if you have a minute, Thank you.
[u][b]Server Background[/b][/u]
The RSPS will be a 2008 economy based server with plenty of emphasis on both Skilling, PvM & PvP. It will most likely feature a client version between 500-600.
[u][b]3 Quick Questions[/b][/u]
1) What do you people look for in an RSPS name? 2) Do you have any suggestions for an RSPS name? (Could be an adjustment of one of mine or entirely your own) 3) Do you like any of the words I've come up with specifically, if so which one and why?
[u][b]Top 3[/b][/u]
[b]Tempest[/b]
[b]Distortion[/b]
[b]Agora[/b]
